snippet.description:
Nepali Song Lyrical Video "Kodo Fulyo Barima" By Udit Narayan Jha & Deepa Jha only on Music Nepal official YouTube channel.

Unauthorized downloading and duplicating on YouTube channel may lead to claim/strike by YouTube.

Nepali Song - Kodo Fulyo Barima
Movie - Muglan
➤ Singer – Udit Narayan Jha & Deepa Jha
➤ Lyrics – Loknath Sapkota
➤ Music – Suresh Adhikari
➤ Editor – Rabin Deshar

Lyrics :- 

चरी र रि ररि रै 
वर्ष र दिनको  
रमाइलो चाड 
गाँउघरमा आइपुग्यो
नेपालीजनको महान् पर्व आँगनमा आइपुग्यो
हो....दसैँ आयो

कोदो फुल्यो बारीमा
लरी लै 
धानको बाला झुल्यो खेतैमा
कत्ति राम्री देखिन्छौ बरी लै
जमरा र रातो टीकैमा

साइको घडी हातैमा
लरीलै ढाका टोपी ढल्क्यो शिरैमा
तिमीलाई नै सुहाउँछ बरी लै
जमरा र रातो टीकैमा
हो....दसैँ आयो
ला...ला..ला

पिढीँमा बसी औँला भाँची छोराको आउने दिन गन्दैथिन्
दसैँको दिन ति बूढीआमै आइपुग्दा छोरो दङ्गै छिन्

भादौरे झरी सुकेर जाँदा असोजमा नौलो रङ्ग छाउँछ
ठूलाको हाता सानाको माथा आशिष दिँदै दसैँ आउँछ

हे एक्लै भयो चमेली लरी लै
राख मलाई पिङ्गको सिटैमा
कत्ति राम्री देखिन्छौ जमरा र रातो टीकैमा

फुल्दछन् खुसी जमराभरि
निधारमा अक्षता हाँस्दछन्
हो फुल्दछन् खुसी जमराभरि
निधारमा अक्षता हाँस्दछन्
मुगलानै जाने आफन्तलाई 
घर आऊ भनी डाक्दछन्
हो.. ती पल्ला घरे लाहुरेदाइले
परदेशको कोसेली बाँड्दैछन्
लाहुरेनी भाउजू मुसुमुसु हाँस्दै
भित्र र बाहिर गर्दैछन्

कोदो फुल्यो बारीमा लरी लै
धानको बाला झुल्यो खेतैमा
नेपालीलाई सुहाँउछ बरी लै 
जमरा र रातो टीकैमा
हो....दसैँ आयो

नेपालीजनको महान् पर्व आँगनमा आइपुग्यो
हो....दसैँ आयो

कोदो फुल्यो बारीमा
लरी लै 
धानको बाला झुल्यो खेतैमा
कत्ति राम्री देखिन्छौ बरी लै
जमरा र रातो टीकैमा

साइको घडी हातैमा
लरीलै ढाका टोपी ढल्क्यो शिरैमा
तिमीलाई नै सुहाउँछ बरी लै
जमरा र रातो टीकैमा
हो....दसैँ आयो
ला...ला..ला

पिढीँमा बसी औँला भाँची छोराको आउने दिन गन्दैथिन्
दसैँको दिन ति बूढीआमै आइपुग्दा छोरो दङ्गै छिन्

भादौरे झरी सुकेर जाँदा असोजमा नौलो रङ्ग छाउँछ
ठूलाको हाता सानाको माथा आशिष दिँदै दसैँ आउँछ

हे एक्लै भयो चमेली लरी लै
राख मलाई पिङ्गको सिटैमा
कत्ति राम्री देखिन्छौ जमरा र रातो टीकैमा

फुल्दछन् खुसी जमराभरि
निधारमा अक्षता हाँस्दछन्
हो फुल्दछन् खुसी जमराभरि
निधारमा अक्षता हाँस्दछन्
मुगलानै जाने आफन्तलाई 
घर आऊ भनी डाक्दछन्
हो.. ती पल्ला घरे लाहुरेदाइले
परदेशको कोसेली बाँड्दैछन्
लाहुरेनी भाउजू मुसुमुसु हाँस्दै
भित्र र बाहिर गर्दैछन्

कोदो फुल्यो बारीमा लरी लै
धानको बाला झुल्यो खेतैमा
नेपालीलाई सुहाँउछ बरी लै 
जमरा र रातो टीकैमा
हो....दसैँ आयो
 
दसैँ आयो

snippet.title: Avatar: Fire and Ash | New Trailer
snippet.description:
This world is much deeper than you imagine. Watch the brand-new trailer for Avatar: Fire and Ash and experience it in theatres December 19th.

Also, don’t miss Avatar: The Way of Water back on the big screen in 3D for one week only, starting October 3rd.

With “Avatar: Fire and Ash,” James Cameron takes audiences back to Pandora in an immersive new adventure with Marine turned Na’vi leader Jake Sully (Sam Worthington), Na’vi warrior Neytiri (Zoe Saldaña), and the Sully family. The film, which has a screenplay by James Cameron & Rick Jaffa & Amanda Silver, and a story by James Cameron & Rick Jaffa & Amanda Silver & Josh Friedman & Shane Salerno, also stars Sigourney Weaver, Stephen Lang, Oona Chaplin, Cliff Curtis, Joel David Moore, CCH Pounder, Edie Falco, David Thewlis, Jemaine Clement, Giovanni Ribisi, Britain Dalton, Jamie Flatters, Trinity Jo-Li Bliss, Jack Champion, Brendan Cowell, Bailey Bass, Filip Geljo, Duane Evans, Jr., and Kate Winslet.

——
ABOUT AVATAR
Director: James Cameron
Cast: Sam Worthington, Zoe Saldaña, Sigourney Weaver, Stephen Lang

ANSHUL GARG presents

PRODUCED BY: Anshul Garg, Dinesh Jain

Special Thanks: Virgin Music India

Virgin Music India Team :-
Head : Amit Sharma 
Team : Nagesh Jadhav, Kajal Israni, Amol Suryavanshi, Lavanya Das & Nishtha Sikroria

Lyrics :- 
Sath Pheron Se Bandha
Janmo Ka Ye Bandhan
Pyar Se Joda Hai Rabb Ne
Preet Ka Daman 
Hai Nayi Rasme, Nayi Kasame
Nayi Uljhan
Hont Hai Khamosh
Lekin Keh Rahi Dhakan

Tere naam ke harf ki tasbeeh ko, saanson
Ke gale ka haar kiya, duniya bhooli aur sirf
tujhe haan sirf tujhe hi pyar kiya

Tum jeet gaye hum hare, 
Tum jeet gaye hum hare, hum hare aur tum jeete
Mere dil ki dil se tauba, dil se tauba mere Dil ki
Dil ki tauba hai dil ab pyar dobara na hoga

Bol kaffara kaffara
Bol kaffara kaffara
Bol o yaara o yaara
Bol kaffara kya hoga

Humne dhadkan dhadkan karke,
dil tere dil se jod liya
Ankhon ne ankhen padh padh ke, 
tujhe vird bana ke yaad kiya

Tujhe pyaar kiya toh tu hi bata, hum ne kya koi jurm kiya
Or jurm kiya hai toh bhi bata, ye jurm ki jurm ki kya hai sazaa

Tumhe hum se badh kar duniya, duniya tumhe humse badhkar
Dil galti kar baitha hai,galti kar baitha hai dil
Haaye dil galti kar baitha tu bol kaffara kya hoga

Bol kaffara kaffara
Bol kaffara kaffara
Bol o yaara o yaara
Bol kaffara kya hoga

Dhadkan meri dhadkan
Dhadkan meri dhadkan
Dhadkan ………

snippet.title: नवरात्रि स्पेशल :ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी | Durga Mata Aarti | Om Jai Ambe Gauri | Durga Ma Ki Aarti
snippet.description:
नवरात्रि स्पेशल : ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी | Durga Mata Aarti | Om Jai Ambe Gauri | Durga Ma Ki Aarti

Description:
Welcome to this divine rendition of ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी — the powerful Durga Mata Aarti that invokes the blessings of Maa Durga during the auspicious occasion of Navratri. This Durga Ma Ki Aarti is filled with devotion and praise, making it an ideal way to worship Goddess Durga and seek her blessings for strength, prosperity, and peace.

🌸 ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी is a traditional prayer sung with love and reverence to honor Goddess Durga, who is revered as the embodiment of Shakti (power). The Aarti resonates with a divine energy, especially during the Navratri festival, when devotees come together to celebrate the nine days of the goddess.

🔔 This Navratri special video will fill your heart with positivity, divine energy, and spiritual peace. Whether you are participating in the Navratri celebrations or seeking to connect with the divine energy of Maa Durga, this Aarti will bring you closer to the goddess.

✨ Submerge yourself in the divine melody of Maa Durga's Aarti and experience her powerful presence in your life.

🔔 Don't forget to subscribe, like, and share this video with your friends and family to spread the divine blessings of Durga Ma.

🕉️ Om Jai Ambe Gauri – Jai Maa Durga! 🕉️

Description:
Welcome to this divine rendition of ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी — the powerful Durga Mata Aarti that invokes the blessings of Maa Durga during the auspicious occasion of Navratri. This Durga Ma Ki Aarti is filled with devotion and praise, making it an ideal way to worship Goddess Durga and seek her blessings for strength, prosperity, and peace.

🌸 ॐ जय अम्बे गौरी is a traditional prayer sung with love and reverence to honor Goddess Durga, who is revered as the embodiment of Shakti (power). The Aarti resonates with a divine energy, especially during the Navratri festival, when devotees come together to celebrate the nine days of the goddess.

🔔 This Navratri special video will fill your heart with positivity, divine energy, and spiritual peace. Whether you are participating in the Navratri celebrations or seeking to connect with the divine energy of Maa Durga, this Aarti will bring you closer to the goddess.

✨ Submerge yourself in the divine melody of Maa Durga's Aarti and experience her powerful presence in your life.

🔔 Don't forget to subscribe, like, and share this video with your friends and family to spread the divine blessings of Durga Ma.

snippet.title: HAQ | Official Teaser | Yami Gautam Dhar, Emraan Hashmi | Suparn S Varma | In Cinemas 7th Nov
snippet.description:
Shazia Bano takes her husband Abbas to court after he abandons her and their children, sparking a national battle over faith, women’s rights, and justice. Inspired by the landmark Supreme Court judgement of Mohd. Ahmed Khan vs. Shah Bano Begum. Haq is the story of one woman’s fight for her rights and justice. 

Releasing in cinemas on 7th November

HAQ is a fictionalized and dramatized version of events stated in the book titled ‘Bano: Bharat ki Beti’ written by Jigna Vora.

Cast- Yami Gautam, Emraan Hashmi, Vartika Singh, Danish Husain, Sheeba Chadha,
Aseem Hattangady
Directed by- Suparn S Varma
Written by- Reshu Nath
Produced by- Vineet Jain
Produced by- Vishal Gurnani, Juhi Parekh Mehta, Harman Baweja
Co- Producer- Amrita Pandey
Co-Producer- Suparn S Varma, Rowena Baweja, Sandeep Singh
Supervising Producer (Insomnia Films)- Vicky Jain

Director of Photography- Pratham Mehta
Associate Producer- Kalpesh Damani
Supervising Producer- Shraddha Chauhan
Executive Producers- Ramesh G Yadav, Priyanka Mehrotra
Production Designers- Abhijit Gaonkar, Sonam Singh
Costume Designer- Ashley Rebello
Casting Director- Shivam Gupta
Editor- Ninad Khanolkar
Background Music- Sandeep Chowta
Lyrics- Kaushal Kishore
Music- Vishal Mishra
Sound Designer- Ajay Kumar PB
Supervising Colorist- Sidharth Meer
Associate Directors- Ashish Prashar, Manya Mirchandani
DI Studio- Bridge Postworks
VFX Studio- White Apple Studio
Chief Business Officer- Mamta Kamtikar
VP, Marketing- Ishwinder Arora
Chief Finance Officer- Mukesh Jain

Tune into Saiyaara Reprise and feel it all again ✨

🎬 Movie Credits:

Starring: Ahaan Panday, Aneet Padda

Producer: Akshaye Widhani

Story And Screenplay: Sankalp Sadanah
Dialogues: Rohan Shankar
Associate Producer: Rishabh Chopra
Creative Executive Producer: Sumana Ghosh

Trailers & Promos: Mohit Sajnaney
Release Date: 18 July 2025

Synopsis:
Yash Raj Films’ Saiyaara is an intense love story, that launches Ahaan Panday and Aneet Padda as the next YRF hero and heroine respectively. 

Directed by Mohit Suri, a master of the romance genre, Saiyaara tells a pure-hearted love story of two youngsters Vaani and Krish. While Vaani writes, Krish sings and they both make music together. Though poles apart in their lives, beliefs and backgrounds, Vaani and Krish are perfect with each other and for each other. Will they understand that truth despite their age, their problems? 

They say flawed, imperfect people make for a perfect love story…and Saiyaara is about celebrating that one love story that is so deep, so pure and so caring that it is absolutely unconditional.

Vaani and Krish will have to navigate life, their problems, their insecurities to hopefully realise that only love can be the answer to everything. Saiyaara is a film that celebrates every season of love through the eyes of Vaani & Krish and poses a simple question…do you love someone so much that you would bet everything to keep that person in your life?

Synopsis:
Yash Raj Films’ Saiyaara is an intense love story, that launches Ahaan Panday and Aneet Padda as the next YRF hero and heroine respectively. 

Directed by Mohit Suri, a master of the romance genre, Saiyaara tells a pure-hearted love story of two youngsters Vaani and Krish. While Vaani writes, Krish sings and they both make music together. Though poles apart in their lives, beliefs and backgrounds, Vaani and Krish are perfect with each other and for each other. Will they understand that truth despite their age, their problems? 

They say flawed, imperfect people make for a perfect love story…and Saiyaara is about celebrating that one love story that is so deep, so pure and so caring that it is absolutely unconditional.

Vaani and Krish will have to navigate life, their problems, their insecurities to hopefully realise that only love can be the answer to everything. Saiyaara is a film that celebrates every season of love through the eyes of Vaani & Krish and poses a simple question…do you love someone so much that you would bet everything to keep that person in your life?

snippet.title: PERFECT - Guru Randhawa, Varun Dhawan, Janhvi Kapoor | Sunny Sanskari Ki Tulsi Kumari
snippet.description:
Sir to pairan de takk,
You so perfect! 💯

Adding to the fire of ‘Sunny Sanskari Ki Tulsi Kumari’, Guru Randhawa joins the party with PERFECT! 🔥 Composed and written by Guru Randhawa, Rony Ajnali and Gill Machhrai, the song is sung by Guru Randhawa. Starring our Sunny ‘Varun Dhawan’ and Tulsi ‘Janhvi Kapoor’ in the video, get ready to watch, vibe, and replay on loop! 🚀

#PERFECT #GuruRandhawa #VarunDhawan #janhvikapoor

Sir to pairan de takk
You r so perfect
Pind to shehran de takk
You r so perfect

Kim to v gol lakk
Because You r so perfect
Saare te Tere te jatonde hakk
Because You r so perfect

Sohniye bullan di teri surkhi
Tu patt dita turki
Gall teri turpi

Haye Heer ne a diti tenu gudti
Ni fit Teri kurti
Lata di jiwe murki

Agg lone nakhre ne Patt ta punjab ni
Tuhi kalli dunia te kutt di swaad ni
Tere aage lagde husan saare farzi
Na koi tetho pehla sohni na koi tetho baad ni

Gol gol addian di thakk thakk
You r so perfect
Dressa utte laawe lakh
You r so perfect

Matthe ali teri latt
You r so perfect
Teri juye to v maadi latt
Not so Perfect

Lembo vangu vish vish dharti te ture
Tera Dubbel swing lakk khaye ni
London de sab to mashoor darji to
Gale paan patte ale tu rakaye ni

Akhian to shed shed chakk di nai
Lang jawe Mundyea nu takk di nai
Kade LA kade tu dubai huni ae
Kr kr shoppinga tu thakk di nai

Kacrch di lakh lakh
You r so perfect
Nikl di jach jach
You r so perfect
Teri beauty nu number 10
You r so perfect
Chobaran nu pondi gash
No so perfect

Husna da dang maare Naag di bachi
Toba toba agg kudi banke nachi
Naina ch saroor 7 bottela jinna
Reshami jehe aang odi Umar kachi

Guru nu v maare akh
You r so perfect
Gill Rony laye patt
You r so perfect
Pinda de tu maare jatt
You r so perfect
Tenu maaf ne Qatal 8
Not so perfect

Solti Jeuko Darshana Paiyo

Timi Nai Hau Jibanko Sahara
Soltiniko Darshana Paiyo 
Aba Malai Yo Bhanda K Chaiyo

Timi Bhaye Malai Koi Chaidaina
Solti Jeuko Darshana Paiyo

Soltiniko Darshana Paiyo 
Aba Malai Yo Bhanda K Chaiyo

Solti Jeuko Darshana Paiyo 
Aba Malai Yo Bhanda K Chaiyo

Soltiniko Darshana Paiyo 
Aba Malai Yo Bhanda K Chaiyo

snippet.title: 4k video - सबकोई खेलबै झिझिया - #asgaruwa | puja mandal | ajay anuragi | #suman sona
snippet.description:
मैथिली झिझिया || सबकोई खेलबै झिझिया ||
Singer :-- ajay anuragi/ suman sona
Music :-- pramod ji
Lyris :-- bn. Patel
Ft :-- ajay asgaruwa/ puja mandal
Camera :-- laxmi sahni.. Reyans studio
director :-- ajay asgaruwa
Record :-- reyans recording studio
Coros :-- champa / chameli / jhabri / rachana
Dain cast :-- bijli
Dhami :-- pothiya
Light man :-- sarman hahni / rahul sah
Spacial :- namaste mithila films production / jitendra maithil
Location :-- yatri niwash / mani mandap janakpur dham
................................
#anuragi
#asgaruwa
#asgruwa ke dance
#asgruwakenewcomaday
#asgruwabaladance
#asgruwapujakegeet
#uchhanpurwalikegeet
#datbalikejhijhiyageet
#asgruwakejhijhiygeet
#asgruwakenayavideo
#pujamandal
#ajayasgruwanewsong
#rupansimusic
#jhijhiya
#maithilijhijhiya
#champa
#chameli
#jhabri
#pothiya
#bijli
#रचना

Khel jaichhi jhijhiya ye piya
Khub khelbai jhijhiya 2
Khel jau jhijhiya ye rani 
Khub khelu jhijhiya 2
Dainiyake beta aai martai ki 
Hamsab khelbai jhijhiya
Baso katbaya nai miltai ki ham sab khelbai
Khelbai jhijhiya
Sabkoi kheltai jhijhiya hehe sabkoi kheltai jhijhiya
Dainiya........


Jab jab jadu tona karbe ge dainiya
Tab tab jhijhiya khelbau ge 2
Jhijhiya ke lahasse muh tohar jharkaibauge
Jhijhiyake aaig se kesh tohar jharkaibau ge
Kajar bijar kake tu aibeki hamsab khelbai jhijhiya
Jhijhiya ke bhur tu nai hinheki ham sab khelbai jhijhiya
Sab koi kheltai......

Gharse to nai nikalihe ge dainiya jhijhiya
Pa najar nai lagaihe ge 2
Bhurhiya mai aai hamr jhijhiya ke dhtai ge 
Mahrani maiya aai hamr jhijhiya ke dhekh tai ge
Kotari ke max khake aibe ki ham sab khelbai jhijhiya
Samsan ghatme jake tu nachbe ki ham sab khelbai jhijhiya

snippet.title: Sushant Ghimire - Chitthi (the last letter) | Prod. AVSHK | Official Release | Nahunu ae nirasha
snippet.description:
Wanted to express some words on behalf of those braves who lost their lives in Genz protest. Wherever they are , they might miss home , miss their friends/family , miss everything about being alive . Hope they rest in peace and justice be prevail.

 Chitthi- The last letter ,is a tribute to all of them .

Composed/ Written and Performed by : Sushant Ghimire
Audio Produced by : AVSHK
Mix/Mastered : AVSHK
Recorded at : Esther's Production
Bass Guitar: Dura Himself
Sarod: Sushant Ghimire
Alaap: Rupesh Jha
Back vox: Kaizen , Dura, Rupesh, Sushant.
Artwork : Praeev Shrestha/ Anmol Adhikari

Special Thanks: 
Rijan Maharjan, Bhisma Raj Ghimire.

Lyrics:
Awaz mera gunjiyeki, mai taadhi jaana le
Ki barsau ka yaad ti birsinchau ki, mai chaadi jana le
Chamki rahula ma tara jhai timra
Sparsha chann mera tyahi wari pari
Timro angalo Jhai nyano navayepani
Herirahula ma chamkine gari.... Ma chamkine gari

Baat thiye saatha haru khaasa
feri vetaula katai.....
Aaja nahula kohi majha
Tara mann ma chau sabai
Nahunu ae nirasha....
Ma jaldaigaye ni aaja
yi mera praan saas maa
aago dandani huda ni
siir uthaunu ruda ni

Diyo jhai timi ujyaalo charera
baa aama roye ni afno sahara jalera
thulo manche bannu hai vanthye
timi amar vayeu ni niswartha ladai ladera
feri yo bajrapath kasaima naparos hai
kasaiko sahara aago ma dadaunu naparos hai
eutai binti ki sunchau saba?
kathghara ma nyaya paincha ki aba?

Nahunu ae nirasha....
Ma jaldaigaye ni aaja
yi mera praan saas maa
aago dandani huda ni
Nahunu ae nirasha....
Ma jaldaigaye ni aaja
yi mera praan saas maa
aago dandani huda ni
siir uthaunu ruda ni

Awaz mera gunjiye ki
mai mari jana le.......


©Sushant Ghimire 2025

Unauthorized  replication of any content related to this video is not allowed 🚫

#sushantghimire #chitthi #atribute

मुझे एक है तेरा सहारा॥

snippet.title: Wakka Lagdo Sansar - bekcha - Jodi No.1 Title Song [Lyrical Video]
snippet.description:
#wakkalagdosansar #Jodino1 #bekcha 
Wakka Lagdo Sansar is the original soundtrack for an amazing web series Jodi No. 1 made with love, soul and perseverance by brilliant human beings with big dreams. When you have the time and mind, go catch it here:

The first episode: https://youtu.be/lCakw0IyOt4
Full Channel : https://www.youtube.com/@UC3uDjw2Sg4EgPfZeAR_Q2rQ 

I would like to pay respects to the brave fighters, martyrs of the current movement in Nepal. The whole nation mourns this massive loss and is forever indebted to all of  you.  I am sending out prayers to the bereaved family and friends.

I sit here many miles away wondering what went wrong, why this had to happen and if the unbearable losses had to happen. I fail to make sense of most of it. There is but a glimmer of hope with this morning's announcement. But I still have fear in the back of my mind that things may turn out worse. I hope I am wrong and I hope better days are on the way. Thank you,  Generation Z, all the mighty warriors from September 8, everyone who took part in this revolution. 


Also, I'm not sure right now is a space for me to describe the song. To put it briefly, this expresses frustration and annoyance at how at times the endless torment life can feel like. If this makes you feel worse, maybe come back to the song some other time. The release was planned a week back,  and things went seriously south, but maybe now we shall all slowly resume. Shall come back with more... The official video will be out soon.

Wishing all of you strength, peace and love. Please keep up the kindness, camaraderie and  the big little things. I hope to be able to help in some way.

snippet.title: 2025 विश्वकर्मा पूजा आरती - Vishwakarma Aarti - Rinky Vishwakarma - Vishwakarma Pooja Aarti
snippet.description:
🙏 On the auspicious occasion of Vishwakarma Puja 2025, listen to the soulful Vishwakarma Aarti sung by Rinky Vishwakarma.
This divine aarti is dedicated to Lord Vishwakarma, the celestial architect and creator of the universe.

🌸 2025 विश्वकर्मा पूजा आरती | Vishwakarma Aarti | Rinky Vishwakarma 🌸

🙏 पावन अवसर पर प्रस्तुत है विश्वकर्मा पूजा 2025 की आरती, जिसे मधुर स्वर में गाया है रिंकी विश्वकर्मा ने।
यह दिव्य आरती भगवान विश्वकर्मा जी को समर्पित है, जिन्हें सृष्टि का दिव्य शिल्पकार और देवों के वास्तुकार माना जाता है।

👉 इस आरती को भक्तिभाव से सुनें और Like, Share & Subscribe करना न भूलें।

https://www.instagram.com/reels/audio/1363373145215357/

► Song - Vishwakarma Aarti

ॐ जय श्री विश्वकर्मा प्रभु जय श्री विश्वकर्मा
सकल सृष्टि के कर्ता रक्षक श्रुति धर्मा
ॐ जय श्री विश्वकर्मा

आदि सृष्टि में विधि को, श्रुति उपदेश दिया
शिल्प शस्त्र का जग में, ज्ञान विकास किया
ॐ जय श्री विश्वकर्मा

ऋषि अंगिरा ने तप से, शांति नही पाई
ध्यान किया जब प्रभु का, सकल सिद्धि आई
ॐ जय श्री विश्वकर्मा

रोग ग्रस्त राजा ने, जब आश्रय लीना
संकट मोचन बनकर, दूर दुख कीना
ॐ जय श्री विश्वकर्मा

जब रथकार दम्पती, तुमरी टेर करी
सुनकर दीन प्रार्थना, विपत्ति हरी सगरी
ॐ जय श्री विश्वकर्मा

एकानन चतुरानन, पंचानन राजे
द्विभुज, चतुर्भुज, दशभुज, सकल रूप साजे
ॐ जय श्री विश्वकर्मा

ध्यान धरे जब पद का, सकल सिद्धि आवे
मन दुविधा मिट जावे, अटल शांति पावे
ॐ जय श्री विश्वकर्मा

श्री विश्वकर्मा जी की आरती, जो कोई नर गावे
कहत गजानन स्वामी, सुख सम्पत्ति पावे
ॐ जय श्री विश्वकर्मा

ॐ जय श्री विश्वकर्मा प्रभु जय श्री विश्वकर्मा
सकल सृष्टि के कर्ता रक्षक श्रुति धर्मा
ॐ जय श्री विश्वकर्मा

Om Jai Shri Vishwakarma Prabhu Jai Shri Vishwakarma
Sakal Srishti Ke Karta Rakshak Shruti Dharma
Om Jai Shri Vishwakarma

Aadi Srishti Mein Vidhi Ko, Shruti Updesh Diya
Shilp Shastra Ka Jag Mein, Gyaan Vikas Kiya
Om Jai Shri Vishwakarma

Rishi Angira Ne Tap Se, Shaanti Nahi Paayi
Dhyaan Kiya Jab Prabhu Ka, Sakal Siddhi Aayi
Om Jai Shri Vishwakarma

Rog Grast Raja Ne, Jab Aashray Leena
Sankat Mochan Bankar, Door Dukh Keena
Om Jai Shri Vishwakarma

Jab Rathkaar Dampati, Tumri Ter Kari
Sunkar Deen Prarthana, Vipatti Hari Sagari
Om Jai Shri Vishwakarma

Ekanan Chaturanand, Panchanan Raaje
DviBhuja, ChaturBhuja, Dashabhuja, Sakal Roop Saaje
Om Jai Shri Vishwakarma

Dhyaan Dhare Jab Pad Ka, Sakal Siddhi Aave
Man Duvitha Mit Jaave, Atal Shaanti Paave
Om Jai Shri Vishwakarma

Shri Vishwakarma Ji Ki Aarti, Jo Koi Nar Gaave
Kahat Gajanan Swami, Sukh Sampatti Paave
Om Jai Shri Vishwakarma

Om Jai Shri Vishwakarma Prabhu Jai Shri Vishwakarma
Sakal Srishti Ke Karta Rakshak Shruti Dharma
Om Jai Shri Vishwakarma

snippet.description:
तीसरा नवरात्र स्पेशल - नवरात्र के तीसरे दिन चंद्रघंटा माता कथा सुनने से मनोकामनाएं पूर्ण होती है

#navratri 
#माँचंद्रघंटाकीकथा
#chaitranavratri2025 
#navratriday3 
#navratri2025 
#maachandraghanta 
#maachandraghantakikatha

तीसरे नवरात्र  2025 , माँ चंद्रघंटा की कथा,  चंद्रघंटा माता कथा , माँ चंद्रघंटा की कहानी, माता चंद्रघंटा की कथा, Om Jai Chandraghanta Mata , Maa ChandraGhata ki Aarti ,  तीसरा नवरात्रि स्पेशल, महिषासुर, Chandraghanta Mata Katha, मां दुर्गा की तीसरी शक्ति, Navratri 2025 Day 3, Navratri, Navratri Vrat Katha, Navratri 2025 3rd Day, Maa Chandraghanta Vrat Katha, Chandraghanta Mata Ki Katha, Navratri Third Day, माँ चंद्रघंटा की कथा, Navratri 3rd day maa, Matarani Ki katha , Nau Devi katha , Chaitra Navratri Katha , navratri,navratri katha day 3,navratri vrat katha,navratri katha,तीसरे नवरात्र की पौराणिक कथा , chandraghanta mata ki katha - चंद्रघंटा माता की कहानी,navratri katha,navratri katha day 2,navratri katha day 4,navratri katha day 6,नवरात्रि के तीसरे दिन माँ चंद्रघंटा की कथा,navratri day 3,durga saptshati katha,navratri day 3- maa chandraghanta ki katha,chandraghanta mata ki katha,maa chandraghanta ki katha,maa katyayani ki katha, play Chandraghanta katha,

snippet.title: Navratri Special श्री दुर्गा चालीसा |नमो दुर्गे सुःख करनी |Namo Namo Durge Sukh Karni |Durga Chalisa
snippet.description:
#durgamaa  #durgachalisa #दुर्गाचालीसा 
Navratri Special श्री दुर्गा चालीसा |नमो दुर्गे सुःख करनी |Namo Namo Durge Sukh Karni |Durga Chalisa
Navratri Special श्री दुर्गा चालीसा |नमो दुर्गे सुःख करनी |Namo Namo Durge Sukh Karni |Durga Chalisa

नमो नमो दुर्गे सुख करनी।
नमो नमो दुर्गे दुःख हरनी॥

निरंकार है ज्योति तुम्हारी।
तिहूं लोक फैली उजियारी॥
शशि ललाट मुख महाविशाला।
नेत्र लाल भृकुटि विकराला॥

रूप मातु को अधिक सुहावे।
दरश करत जन अति सुख पावे॥

तुम संसार शक्ति लै कीना।
पालन हेतु अन्न धन दीना॥

अन्नपूर्णा हुई जग पाला।
तुम ही आदि सुन्दरी बाला॥
प्रलयकाल सब नाशन हारी।
तुम गौरी शिवशंकर प्यारी॥

शिव योगी तुम्हरे गुण गावें।
ब्रह्मा विष्णु तुम्हें नित ध्यावें॥

रूप सरस्वती को तुम धारा।
दे सुबुद्धि ऋषि मुनिन उबारा॥

धरयो रूप नरसिंह को अम्बा।
परगट भई फाड़कर खम्बा॥
रक्षा करि प्रह्लाद बचायो।
हिरण्याक्ष को स्वर्ग पठायो॥

लक्ष्मी रूप धरो जग माहीं।
श्री नारायण अंग समाहीं॥

क्षीरसिन्धु में करत विलासा।
दयासिन्धु दीजै मन आसा॥

हिंगलाज में तुम्हीं भवानी।
महिमा अमित न जात बखानी॥
मातंगी अरु धूमावति माता।
भुवनेश्वरी बगला सुख दाता॥

श्री भैरव तारा जग तारिणी।
छिन्न भाल भव दुःख निवारिणी॥

केहरि वाहन सोह भवानी।
लांगुर वीर चलत अगवानी॥

कर में खप्पर खड्ग विराजै।
जाको देख काल डर भाजै॥
सोहै अस्त्र और त्रिशूला।
जाते उठत शत्रु हिय शूला॥

नगरकोट में तुम्हीं विराजत।
तिहुंलोक में डंका बाजत॥

शुंभ निशुंभ दानव तुम मारे।
रक्तबीज शंखन संहारे॥

महिषासुर नृप अति अभिमानी।
जेहि अघ भार मही अकुलानी॥
रूप कराल कालिका धारा।
सेन सहित तुम तिहि संहारा॥

परी गाढ़ संतन पर जब जब।
भई सहाय मातु तुम तब तब॥

अमरपुरी अरु बासव लोका।
तब महिमा सब रहें अशोका॥

ज्वाला में है ज्योति तुम्हारी।
तुम्हें सदा पूजें नर-नारी॥
प्रेम भक्ति से जो यश गावें।
दुःख दारिद्र निकट नहिं आवें॥

ध्यावे तुम्हें जो नर मन लाई।
जन्म-मरण ताकौ छुटि जाई॥

जोगी सुर मुनि कहत पुकारी।
योग न हो बिन शक्ति तुम्हारी॥

शंकर आचारज तप कीनो।
काम अरु क्रोध जीति सब लीनो॥
निशिदिन ध्यान धरो शंकर को।
काहु काल नहिं सुमिरो तुमको॥

शक्ति रूप का मरम न पायो।
शक्ति गई तब मन पछितायो॥

शरणागत हुई कीर्ति बखानी।
जय जय जय जगदम्ब भवानी॥

भई प्रसन्न आदि जगदम्बा।
दई शक्ति नहिं कीन विलम्बा॥
मोको मातु कष्ट अति घेरो।
तुम बिन कौन हरै दुःख मेरो॥

आशा तृष्णा निपट सतावें।
रिपू मुरख मौही डरपावे॥

शत्रु नाश कीजै महारानी।
सुमिरौं इकचित तुम्हें भवानी॥

करो कृपा हे मातु दयाला।
ऋद्धि-सिद्धि दै करहु निहाला।
जब लगि जिऊं दया फल पाऊं ।
तुम्हरो यश मैं सदा सुनाऊं ॥

दुर्गा चालीसा जो कोई गावै।
सब सुख भोग परमपद पावै॥

देवीदास शरण निज जानी।
करहु कृपा जगदम्ब भवानी॥

जाते उठत शत्रु हिय शूला॥

नगरकोट में तुम्हीं विराजत।
तिहुंलोक में डंका बाजत॥

शुंभ निशुंभ दानव तुम मारे।
रक्तबीज शंखन संहारे॥

महिषासुर नृप अति अभिमानी।
जेहि अघ भार मही अकुलानी॥
रूप कराल कालिका धारा।
सेन सहित तुम तिहि संहारा॥

परी गाढ़ संतन पर जब जब।
भई सहाय मातु तुम तब तब॥

अमरपुरी अरु बासव लोका।
तब महिमा सब रहें अशोका॥

ज्वाला में है ज्योति तुम्हारी।
तुम्हें सदा पूजें नर-नारी॥
प्रेम भक्ति से जो यश गावें।
दुःख दारिद्र निकट नहिं आवें॥

ध्यावे तुम्हें जो नर मन लाई।
जन्म-मरण ताकौ छुटि जाई॥

जोगी सुर मुनि कहत पुकारी।
योग न हो बिन शक्ति तुम्हारी॥

शंकर आचारज तप कीनो।
काम अरु क्रोध जीति सब लीनो॥
निशिदिन ध्यान धरो शंकर को।
काहु काल नहिं सुमिरो तुमको॥

शक्ति रूप का मरम न पायो।
शक्ति गई तब मन पछितायो॥

शरणागत हुई कीर्ति बखानी।
जय जय जय जगदम्ब भवानी॥

भई प्रसन्न आदि जगदम्बा।
दई शक्ति नहिं कीन विलम्बा॥
मोको मातु कष्ट अति घेरो।
तुम बिन कौन हरै दुःख मेरो॥

आशा तृष्णा निपट सतावें।
रिपू मुरख मौही डरपावे॥

शत्रु नाश कीजै महारानी।
सुमिरौं इकचित तुम्हें भवानी॥

करो कृपा हे मातु दयाला।
ऋद्धि-सिद्धि दै करहु निहाला।
जब लगि जिऊं दया फल पाऊं ।
तुम्हरो यश मैं सदा सुनाऊं ॥

दुर्गा चालीसा जो कोई गावै।
सब सुख भोग परमपद पावै॥

देवीदास शरण निज जानी।
करहु कृपा जगदम्ब भवानी॥

У цьому відео я прокачую обліковий запис нуба першого рівня до максимального професіонала за допомогою спорядження OP: проклятої подвійної катани, гітари-черепа, покращеного карате-акули та раси v4, використовуючи лише фрукти, що з'являються за допомогою сповіщення про фрукти в Blox Fruits.

Приєднуйтесь до групи! https://www.roblox.com/groups/34051758/Meteorics-Galaxy#!/about

Приєднуйтесь до Discord! https://discord.gg/3QbWEBjseh

pt-BR.title: Noob To Max com apenas FRUIT NOTIFIER no Blox Fruits
pt-BR.description:
Neste vídeo, levo uma conta de iniciante de nível um até uma conta profissional de nível máximo com um conjunto OP de katana dupla amaldiçoada, guitarra de caveira, caratê do homem-tubarão aprimorado e corrida v4, usando apenas frutas que aparecem usando o notificador de frutas do Blox Fruits.

Entre no grupo! https://www.roblox.com/groups/34051758/Meteorics-Galaxy#!/about

Entre no Discord! https://discord.gg/3QbWEBjseh

en.title: Noob To Max With Only FRUIT NOTIFIER In Blox Fruits
en.description:
In this video I bring a level one noob account all the way to a max level pro with an OP loadout of cursed dual katana, skull guitar, upgraded sharkman karate, and race v4 by only using fruits that spawn using the fruit notifier in Blox Fruits.

Join the group! https://www.roblox.com/groups/34051758/Meteorics-Galaxy#!/about

Join the discord! https://discord.gg/3QbWEBjseh

de-DE.title: Von Noob bis Max mit nur FRUIT NOTIFIER in Blox Fruits
de-DE.description:
In diesem Video bringe ich einen Noob-Account der Stufe 1 zum Profi-Account der höchsten Stufe mit einem OP-Loadout aus verfluchtem Doppelkatana, Totenkopfgitarre, verbessertem Sharkman-Karate und Rennen V4, indem ich nur Früchte verwende, die über den Fruchtbenachrichtiger in Blox Fruits erscheinen.


Tretet der Gruppe bei! https://www.roblox.com/groups/34051758/Meteorics-Galaxy#!/about


Tretet dem Discord bei! https://discord.gg/3QbWEBjseh

hi.title: ब्लॉक्स फ़्रूट्स में सिर्फ़ फ़्रूट नोटिफ़ायर से नौसिखिए से अधिकतम तक
hi.description:
इस वीडियो में, मैं लेवल वन के नौसिखिए अकाउंट को अधिकतम लेवल प्रो तक ले जा रहा हूँ, जिसमें शापित डुअल कटाना, स्कल गिटार, अपग्रेडेड शार्कमैन कराटे और रेस v4 का ओपी लोडआउट है, और वह भी केवल ब्लॉक्स फ्रूट्स में फ्रूट नोटिफ़ायर से उत्पन्न होने वाले फलों का उपयोग करके।

ग्रुप में शामिल हों! https://www.roblox.com/groups/34051758/Meteorics-Galaxy#!/about

डिस्कॉर्ड में शामिल हों! https://discord.gg/3QbWEBjseh

te.title: బ్లాక్స్ ఫ్రూట్స్‌లో కేవలం ఫ్రూట్ నోటిఫైయర్‌తో నూబ్ టు మ్యాక్స్
te.description:
ఈ వీడియోలో నేను బ్లాక్స్ ఫ్రూట్స్‌లో ఫ్రూట్ నోటిఫైయర్‌ని ఉపయోగించి స్పాన్ చేసే పండ్లను మాత్రమే ఉపయోగించడం ద్వారా కర్స్డ్ డ్యూయల్ కటానా, స్కల్ గిటార్, అప్‌గ్రేడ్ చేసిన షార్క్‌మ్యాన్ కరాటే మరియు రేస్ v4 యొక్క OP లోడ్‌అవుట్‌తో లెవల్ వన్ నూబ్ ఖాతాను గరిష్ట స్థాయి ప్రోకి తీసుకువస్తున్నాను.

గ్రూప్‌లో చేరండి! https://www.roblox.com/groups/34051758/Meteorics-Galaxy#!/about

డిస్కార్డ్‌లో చేరండి! https://discord.gg/3QbWEBjseh

ko.title: Blox Fruits에서 FRUIT NOTIFIER만 사용하여 Noob To Max를 만드세요
ko.description:
이 영상에서는 Blox Fruits의 과일 알림 기능을 사용하여 생성되는 과일만 사용하여 저주받은 듀얼 카타나, 스컬 기타, 업그레이드된 샤크맨 가라테, 레이스 V4 등 OP 장비를 장착하고 레벨 1 초보자 계정을 최대 레벨 프로 계정까지 키워봅니다.

그룹에 가입하세요! https://www.roblox.com/groups/34051758/Meteorics-Galaxy#!/about

디스코드에 가입하세요! https://discord.gg/3QbWEBjseh

nl-NL.title: Van Noob tot Max met alleen FRUIT NOTIFIER in Blox Fruits
nl-NL.description:
In deze video til ik een level 1 noob-account helemaal op tot een max level pro met een OP-uitrusting bestaande uit Cursed Dual Katana, Skull Guitar, geüpgrade Sharkman Karate en Race V4. Dit doe ik door alleen fruit te gebruiken dat spawnt via de Fruit Notifier in Blox Fruits.

Word lid van de groep! https://www.roblox.com/groups/34051758/Meteorics-Galaxy#!/about

Word lid van de Discord! https://discord.gg/3QbWEBjseh

ja.title: Blox Fruitsでフルーツ通知機能のみを使用して初心者から最高レベルまで
ja.description:
この動画では、レベル1の初心者アカウントを、呪われた二刀流刀、スカルギター、アップグレードされたシャークマンカラテ、そしてレースV4という最強装備で、Blox Fruitsのフルーツ通知機能で出現するフルーツのみを使って、最高レベルのプロにまで育て上げます。

グループに参加しよう！ https://www.roblox.com/groups/34051758/Meteorics-Galaxy#!/about

Discordに参加しよう！ https://discord.gg/3QbWEBjseh

ar.title: من Noob إلى Max باستخدام FRUIT NOTIFIER فقط في Blox Fruits
ar.description:
في هذا الفيديو، أُحسّن حسابي من مستوى مبتدئ إلى مستوى احترافي بمعدات قوية جدًا، تتضمن سيف كاتانا مزدوجًا ملعونًا، وجيتار جمجمة، وكاراتيه شاركمان مُحسّن، وسباق الإصدار الرابع، باستخدام الفواكه التي تظهر فقط باستخدام مُنبه الفواكه في لعبة بلوكس فروتس.

انضم إلى المجموعة! https://www.roblox.com/groups/34051758/Meteorics-Galaxy#!/about
